# Normalize line endings on commit. Without this, a contributor on Windows (or a tool
# that writes files with the platform default) can commit CRLF — which for a Dockerfile
# or a shell script is not cosmetic: YAMLlint rejects CRLF workflows, and `docker-entrypoint.sh`
# with CRLF fails at runtime with `$'\r': command not found`.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Never touch binaries.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.ico binary
*.whl binary
